      "intro": "If your loved one has Medicare or will soon become eligible for Medicare, HIICAP provides free, confidential counseling to help them understand their coverage options. Nearly 500 trained counselors across New York offer one-on-one guidance on Medicare Advantage plans, Medigap policies, prescription drug coverage, and Medicare costs, with no sales pressure or bias toward any insurance company.\n\nBecause Medicare plan choices and costs can change from year to year, many families find it difficult to compare coverage options and determine what best meets their needs. HIICAP counselors can help your loved one understand their current coverage, compare available plan options, resolve health insurance problems, and learn about programs that may help reduce Medicare costs. They can also provide information about other assistance programs and help explain Medicare-related paperwork and processes.",
