      "shortName": "Meals on Wheels EISEP",
      "tagline": "Home-delivered meals may be available Monday through Friday for older adults who have difficulty preparing meals on their own due to illness, disability, or age-related limitations. In many New York communities, the suggested contribution is about $4 per meal, but no one is denied service because they cannot contribute. Meal availability, delivery schedules, and suggested contributions may vary by county.",
